{"tid":1171133,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"識人好過識字 點解仲會有人拎三大個名打飛機？","createTime":"2019-05-25T13:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T00:53:47.000Z","uid":247972,"like":13,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"51436b5b8796431cfe852b5872c461f5ccc4547e","tid":1171133,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"唔明點解大家奴性咁重<br />\n諗住讀完書做一世打工（包括專業人士）<br />\n我見好多師兄都有好多其他出路<br />\n搵錢仲多過連登最愛既ACO<br />\n專業人士都應該要搵下新出路<br />\n好似精算師咁 門檻越尼越低 供多於求<br />\n這年頭做front line賺仲多<br />\n我識好多師兄連精算牌都無諗住考<br />\n寧願做名牌保險公司front office<br />\n成日食好西 又多公司活動<br />\n好過係back office 做夠<br />\n<br />\n所以 唔明3大d傻西點解會覺得自己學位好值錢<br />\n<br />\n利申：精算year1"},{"pid":"6eb4e5e9ebbcebf2db68902fe35b9ff53df1062f","tid":1171133,"uid":247972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"*好過back office 做狗"},{"pid":"497a7b40e55dae1c3e7d36a3a830ab66109c83e9","tid":1171133,"uid":137038,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"讀完三大上下莊出去join下活動做下intern咪識人囉"},{"pid":"804a13fbae4f2af7a933c0ed8daf13eaee6f72e3","tid":1171133,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"佢識三大啲人"},{"pid":"4e322fc8ca31b08f42320faefb02dffdecf88b56","tid":1171133,"uid":247972,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"497a7b40e55dae1c3e7d36a3a830ab66109c83e9","tid":1171133,"uid":137038,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"讀完三大上下莊出去join下活動做下intern咪識人囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪3rd hon"},{"pid":"5b7a31bb976e465d6602d9f46f89cd1108a9efa0","tid":1171133,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"804a13fbae4f2af7a933c0ed8daf13eaee6f72e3","tid":1171133,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"佢識三大啲人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"6a